```plantuml
@startuml FPriv_factom-harmony-connect-python-sdk
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

package "Factom SDK" {
    [FactomClient] <<Facade>> 
    [ChainsClient]
    [EntriesClient]
    [IdentitiesClient]
    [ApiInfoClient]
    [ReceiptsClient]
    [AnchorsClient]
    [Utils]
    [KeyCommon]
    [ValidateSignatureUtil]
    [CommonUtil]
    [Request Handler]

    [FactomClient] --> [ChainsClient]
    [FactomClient] --> [EntriesClient]
    [FactomClient] --> [IdentitiesClient]
    [FactomClient] --> [ApiInfoClient]
    [FactomClient] --> [ReceiptsClient]
    [FactomClient] --> [AnchorsClient]
    [FactomClient] --> [Request Handler]

    [ChainsClient] --> [ValidateSignatureUtil]
    [EntriesClient] --> [ValidateSignatureUtil]
    [IdentitiesClient] --> [KeyCommon]
    
    [Request Handler] --> [Utils]
    [Request Handler] --> [CommonUtil]

    [Utils] --> [KeyCommon]
}

package "Sample Application" {
    [simulate_notary.py]
}

[simulate_notary.py] --> [FactomClient]

note right of FactomClient
  Central access point for all SDK functionalities.
  Manages API connection and provides access to client components.
end note

note right of ChainsClient
  Handles chain-related operations.
end note

note right of EntriesClient
  Manages entry-related operations within a chain.
end note

note right of IdentitiesClient
  Manages identity-related operations.
end note

note right of ApiInfoClient
  Retrieves general information about the Connect API.
end note

note right of ReceiptsClient
  Retrieves receipts for entries.
end note

note right of AnchorsClient
  Retrieves anchor information for directory blocks.
end note

note right of Request Handler
  Manages low-level HTTP communication with the API.
end note

@enduml
```